We choose about twenty speakers from among the experts in their discipline and we select them for their charismatic side, he said.
About global warming, "we can talk about hours, but we can also talk about key objectives in a few minutes," said Jean Jouzel, who spoke without notes, but with the help of graphs, in front of about fifty people.
