Either we will give the order to our militants that there are no blockades, no blockade of the supply centers.
But you can always have a few recalcitrants who are not happy, he added.
Philippe Grillot, president of TLF, welcomed "a good agreement", even if it was "difficult to concede increases on high salaries given international competition".
